565
00:25:49,820 --> 00:25:51,610
Your mother has spent half of
her lifetime dancing.

566
00:25:51,730 --> 00:25:53,260
You've also been dancing for years now.

567
00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:54,940
That's how you become good at it.

568
00:25:54,940 --> 00:25:55,540
Am I right?

569
00:25:55,690 --> 00:25:56,540
Be patient.

570
00:25:59,090 --> 00:26:01,180
Father. Do you think that

571
00:26:01,410 --> 00:26:03,740
I should not have organised this?

572
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:08,300
