573
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:10,700
She is also the supervisor
in our theatre now.

574
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:12,020
She should be experienced in this.

575
00:26:12,580 --> 00:26:13,380
Forget it.

576
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,490
She've warned me before that

577
00:26:15,780 --> 00:26:17,020
if she found out anything

578
00:26:17,060 --> 00:26:18,690
other than ballet and my studies,

579
00:26:18,690 --> 00:26:19,980
she'll scold me for sure.

580
00:26:21,460 --> 00:26:22,740
I'll figure out a way on my own.

581
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:39,620
The moves are already very easy.

582
00:26:41,010 --> 00:26:42,130
How can I make them easier?

583
00:26:43,060 --> 00:26:43,820
Tong Tong.

584
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:51,940
Practising?

585
00:26:53,130 --> 00:26:54,380
Point your toes.

586
00:26:54,380 --> 00:26:55,540
Don't be lazy.

587
00:27:02,940 --> 00:27:03,620
Mother.

588
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,140
Do dance troupes visit your theatre

589
00:27:05,140 --> 00:27:07,300
