602
00:27:51,210 --> 00:27:52,580
I think it will help to enhance the play.

603
00:27:52,580 --> 00:27:53,580
We can adjust it slightly.

604
00:27:53,580 --> 00:27:55,580
If we can shorten the script...

605
00:27:55,730 --> 00:27:57,860
I hope that the lighting will be softer.

606
00:27:58,100 --> 00:27:59,420
It's better if it's slightly softer.

607
00:28:00,180 --> 00:28:02,420
Tao Zhu. Who is that?

608
00:28:03,330 --> 00:28:04,530
Senior Xu Ao.

609
00:28:05,850 --> 00:28:06,500
Did you see that?

610
00:28:06,660 --> 00:28:08,050
