611
00:28:08,300 --> 00:28:09,490
he won't even notice me.

612
00:28:14,540 --> 00:28:15,420
Tao Zhu.

613
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,700
Actually, it doesn't matter
if he notices you or not.

614
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:18,730
What matters the most is

615
00:28:18,730 --> 00:28:20,420
you let him see you
at your brightest moment.

616
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:23,420
