620
00:28:29,900 --> 00:28:31,100
I'll practice harder.

621
00:28:32,660 --> 00:28:34,380
One, step and step.

622
00:28:34,690 --> 00:28:36,450
Two, step and step.

623
00:28:36,700 --> 00:28:38,580
Three, step and step.

624
00:28:38,740 --> 00:28:39,900
Four, step...

625
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,980
I'm sorry for stepping on you.

626
00:28:46,500 --> 00:28:47,330
