the school infirmary.

639
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:14,020
It's okay.

640
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:15,290
I'll stop causing delay to the practice.

641
00:29:20,540 --> 00:29:21,380
Tong Xi.

642
00:29:21,860 --> 00:29:23,060
