in the future.

652
00:29:38,860 --> 00:29:40,780
I'll help you to find a solution.

653
00:29:41,060 --> 00:29:43,820
You just need to make
the dance moves easier.

654
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:44,940
I'll find someone for help.

655
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:47,100
I have someone in mind.

656
00:29:57,710 --> 00:30:00,040
[Blue Elephant Books]

657
00:30:10,580 --> 00:30:11,290
Nan Yi.

658
00:30:15,380 --> 00:30:17,380
I have a favour to ask from you.

